{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_06_03",
  "title": "兵藤雫 3話 いつもと違うドキドキ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、今日は本当に\n会いに来てくれて、ありがとうございます……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ thank you so much\nfor coming to see me today…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8710936718,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.6666667,
          "startTime": 5.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに、星見のステージに立てて\n本当に、嬉しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so happy to be back on the\nHoshimi stage after so long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9885609587,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8778.105708,
          "startTime": 19.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.0333328883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "流星群も、花火も、一緒に楽しみましょう……！\nここにいるみんなで、一緒に……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s enjoy the meteor shower and fireworks together…!\nAll of us here‚ together…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.1333340326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（久しぶりの地元ライブで楽しそうだな）\n（メンバーもお客さんも、みんないい笑顔だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She looks so happy to be performing in her hometown again.）\n（The members and the audience all have such great smiles.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4602048555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.6602048555
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.6602048555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく、楽しかった……！\n地元ライブ、大成功……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was so much fun…!\nThe hometown live was a huge success…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2268715221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.8935384431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、雫\nこの後はみんなとお祭りを回るんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ Shizuku.\nYou’re going to walk around the festival with everyone next‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、すぐ、着替える\nその……確認だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I’ll change right away.\nUm… just to confirm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8562595049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.2562597591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも、一緒に\nお祭り、回るんだよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nyou’re coming to the festival with us too‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8229261715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.2562597591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、マネージャーとして\nみんなを人混みに放り出せないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ as your manager‚\nI can’t let you all go into the crowd alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.5098199207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……少し、待ってて\nちょっと楽屋に寄ってくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good… I was a bit worried.\nWait a moment‚ I need to stop by the dressing room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9098196665,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4523.513666900001,
          "startTime": 65.4333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うん？　分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Okay‚ sure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0431532541,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5456.846745900002,
