      "text": "雫はどうだ？　夏といえば――\n雫……？　花火、見なくていいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about you‚ Shizuku? When you think of summer――\nShizuku…? Don't you want to watch the fireworks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3666534424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
