      "text": "そんなに雫に見つめられてたら気になるだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you keep staring at me like that‚ I can't help but notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1309736411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。まだ、言ってなかったけど――\n浴衣、よく似合ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right. I haven't said it yet‚ but――\nYou look great in your yukata.",
